  <brief_title>Electrolyte Profile, Nutritional Status and Ileostomy Formation.</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Ileostomy Formation on Nutritional Status and Electrolyte Profile in Rectosigmoidectomy Patients: a Prospective Randomized Trial.</official_title>
